<a class="title" href="/nodes/97206/comments/1433280">Re: Comment savoir ?</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/sufflope" rel="author">Sufflope</a> (<a href="http://bour.name">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2013-02-26T18:00:30+01:00"><span class="date">le 26/02/13</span> <span class="time">à 18:00</span></time>.
