<a class="title" href="/nodes/97206/comments/1433262">Rootkit dans GCC</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/jepostesurlatribune" rel="author">jepostesurlatribune</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-02-26T17:12:56+01:00"><span class="date">le 26/02/13</span> <span class="time">à 17:12</span></time>.
