<a class="title" href="/nodes/97206/comments/1433528">Re: Pas sous linux, mais…</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/pmanglade" rel="author">ǝpɐןƃu∀ nǝıɥʇʇɐW-ǝɹɹǝıԀ</a> (<a href="http://anglade.googlepages.com">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2013-02-27T20:26:53+01:00"><span class="date">le 27/02/13</span> <span class="time">à 20:26</span></time>.
