</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/guolang" rel="author">Grégoire G</a> (<a href="http://guolang.gites-voyages.com">page perso</a>) <time class="updated" datetime="2013-03-01T04:15:45+01:00"><span class="date">le 01/03/13</span> <span class="time">à 04:15</span></time>.
